-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This Software interacts with third-party firewall applications and operating
system components that are distributed under their own respective licenses.
The authors and contributors of this Software make no representations or
warranties regarding these third-party components and are not responsible for
any bugs, security vulnerabilities, behavioral changes, or incompatibilities
in these components. The Software's correct operation depends on the correct
functioning of these underlying tools and the operating system kernel.

Users are responsible for reviewing and complying with the license terms of
all dependencies, including but not limited to:

  - iptables / xtables — GPLv2 (https://www.netfilter.org/)
  - nftables (nft) — GPLv2 (https://www.netfilter.org/projects/nftables/)
  - firewalld — GPLv2+ (https://firewalld.org/)
  - ufw (Uncomplicated Firewall) — GPLv3 (https://launchpad.net/ufw)
  - ipset — GPLv2 (https://ipset.netfilter.org/)
  - Python 3.12+ — PSF License (https://www.python.org/psf/license/)
  - Python Standard Library — PSF License
  - threading, subprocess, os — Python Standard Library
  - shutil, pathlib, tarfile — Python Standard Library

The inclusion of or reliance on these dependencies does not extend this
License to those components, nor does it alter the license terms under which
those components are distributed.

